  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p736512/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201506/d64c200604c84fe591cd815c452334eb.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">No longer will we have to buy an&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/overpriced\" target=\"_blank\">overpriced</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;coffee to get a&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/rubbish\" target=\"_blank\">rubbish</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;wireless internet connection. </span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">我们再也不用为了获得渣速的无线互联网连接而花钱买难喝的咖啡了。</span></p>\n<p>\n\tGoogle is rolling out free wifi in New York as part of a trial the company hopes will eventually <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/span\" target=\"_blank\">span</a> across the whole of the world.目前，谷歌向纽约全市提供免费公共WiFi，而这只是试水，谷歌意图将该计划覆盖全球。</p>\n<p>\n\tThe internet <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/giant\" target=\"_blank\">giant</a> has even gone as far as to set up a company specifically <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/dedicated\" target=\"_blank\">dedicated</a> to the task, called Sidewalk Labs.这家互联网巨头为了完成这一计划甚至还成立了专门的公司，名字就叫人行道实验室（Sidewalk Labs）。</p>\n<p>\n\tHow will they do this you ask &ndash; through turning 10,000 of the big apple&rsquo;s old phone <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/booth\" target=\"_blank\">booth</a>s into ad-supported &lsquo;Wi-Fi <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/pylon\" target=\"_blank\">pylons</a>&rsquo;.你或许会问，谷歌要如何完成这一计划？他们的做法是把纽约市里多达1万个的老旧电话亭改装成带数字面板和大型广告牌的&ldquo;柱子&rdquo;，这些&ldquo;柱子&rdquo;将为附近一定范围内的区域提供免费WiFi。</p>\n<p>\n\tThese converted booths are also intended to provide cell-phone charging, free <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/domestic\" target=\"_blank\">domestic</a> phone calls and a touch screen information hub about the city and transit directions.这些改装后的&ldquo;柱子&rdquo;，其功能还包括免费手机充电、拨打市内电话、上网，以及获取本地服务和信息等。</p>\n<p>\n\tAccording to Bloomberg News, these &lsquo;pylons&rsquo; will be rolled out across New York this autumn.根据彭博社新闻报道，这些&ldquo;柱子&rdquo;将于今秋入驻纽约全市。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p736512/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p736512\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736813/\">全美同性恋婚姻合法 gay的多种表达方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736769/\">帅就一个字！陈坤孔雀大表哥出演阿玛尼广告</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736439/\">这些耳熟能详的经贸术语 你真的了解？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736148/\">双语美文：梦想还是要有的（有声）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736568/\">美男子！最帅大猩猩引女游客排队追捧</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736471/\">“委屈猫”走红网络：可怜小眼神萌杀网友</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736863/\">知道Uber，但不知道ubersexual</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p161331/\">新概念英语第一册Lesson 1  Excuse me</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736266/\">组图：放慢你的脚步 享受一次缓慢旅行</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736804/\">亚投行即将签署协议 中国将成第一大股东</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;